articles.headline: Kyler Fackrell put on IR, leaving New York Giants thin at LB position
articles.description: The New York Giants placed starting outside linebacker Kyler Fackrell on injured reserve Tuesday with a calf injury.

images.alt: Kyler Fackrell put on IR, leaving New York Giants thin at LB position

articles.headline: Source: Ravens head off to Pittsburgh after no new positive COVID-19 tests
articles.description: The Ravens are headed to Pittsburgh after no players tested positive for COVID-19 on Tuesday, a source confirmed.

images.alt: Source: Ravens head off to Pittsburgh after no new positive COVID-19 tests

articles.headline: Inside the outbreak: The latest in the Ravens' COVID-19 saga
articles.description: With now 20 players on the reserve/COVID-19 list, the Ravens' schedule is seeing a domino effect of postponements.

images.alt: Inside the outbreak: The latest in the Ravens' COVID-19 saga

articles.headline: Philadelphia Eagles coach Doug Pederson given no assurance he'll finish season
articles.description: Eagles coach Doug Pederson said he has no assurances from the front office that he will keep his job through the remainder of the season.

images.alt: Philadelphia Eagles coach Doug Pederson given no assurance he'll finish season

articles.headline: San Francisco 49ers' Kyle Shanahan says Arizona 'best scenario for us'
articles.description: The 49ers are moving their entire football operation to Arizona for at least the duration of COVID-19 restrictions in Santa Clara County.

images.alt: San Francisco 49ers' Kyle Shanahan says Arizona 'best scenario for us'
